high_descs: Turn around and turn right to the table.
Pick up the credit card on the table.
Turn left and go to the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a credit card with the lamp light.

high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the end of the coffee table.
Pick up the red credit card off of the coffee table.
Turn left and walk over to the tall lamp in the corner of the room.
Turn on the light of the tall lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a red credit card in the light of a tall lamp.

high_descs: Turn around and take a step then turn right.
Pick up the credit card that's in front of you on the coffee table.
Turn left and walk to the couch then take a step to your left to face the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Inspect a credit card by lamp light.
